==网络审查争议==
{{main|中华人民共和国网络审查}} 
随着中国[[互联网|互联网]]的快速发展，信息的自由传播对中共维持执政地位构成挑战。为了应对来自网络发展形成的影响，中国建立世界上最为先进的[[中华人民共和国网络审查|网络审查制度]]，审查中国大陆的互联网内容，[[防火长城|封锁服务器]]位于境外的政治敏感类网站，以达到其舆论控制的目的。<ref name=":5">{{Cite news|title=中国政府如何审查你的思想？|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-41634026|date=2017-10-16|accessdate=2019-10-27|language=en-GB|first=|last=|author=麥笛文|work=|publisher=英国广播公司|format=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190503025049/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-41634026|archive-date=2019-05-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":43">{{Cite web|title=Why Google Is Quitting China|url=https://www.forbes.com/2010/01/15/baidu-china-search-intelligent-technology-google.html#263cb5418844|accessdate=2019-10-28|author=Rebecca Fannin|date=|last=|first=|format=|work=|publisher=Forbes|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713203611/https://www.forbes.com/2010/01/15/baidu-china-search-intelligent-technology-google.html#263cb5418844|archive-date=2019-07-13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":39">{{Cite web|title=互联网审查工厂：一个有中国特色的新生行业|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/technology/20190102/china-internet-censor/|accessdate=2019-10-27|author=袁莉|date=2019-10-16|last=|format=|work=纽约时报中文网|publisher=|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191015064442/https://cn.nytimes.com/technology/20190102/china-internet-censor/|archive-date=2019-10-15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":35">{{Cite news|title=“翻墙”网民受罚 中国进一步强化网络管控|url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-46823319|date=2019-01-11|accessdate=2019-10-27|language=en-GB|last=斯影|author=|work=|publisher=英国广播公司|format=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190319031148/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-46823319|archive-date=2019-03-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[谷歌退出中国大陆事件|谷歌]]、[[雅虎|雅虎]]等公司退出中国大陆市场。<ref name=":43" /><ref name=":34">{{Cite web|title=Why Google Quit China—and Why It's Heading Back|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/technology/archive/2016/01/why-google-quit-china-and-why-its-heading-back/424482/|accessdate=2019-10-27|author=|date=2016-01-19|last=Waddell|first=Kaveh|format=|work=The Atlantic|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191025073946/https://www.theatlantic.com/technology/archive/2016/01/why-google-quit-china-and-why-its-heading-back/424482/|archive-date=2019-10-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>与此同时，中国政府还开始雇佣大量[[网络评论员|网络评论员]]（俗称“[[五毛党|五毛党]]”）来控制舆论导向。<ref name=":42">{{Cite web|title=哈佛大学对中国网络“五毛”展开研究|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20160520/c20fiftycent/|accessdate=2019-10-27|author=孟宝勒|date=2016-05-20|last=|format=|work=纽约时报中文网|publisher=|language=zh-hans|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191007013721/https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20160520/c20fiftycent/|archive-date=2019-10-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==控制舆论争议==
美国[[杂志|杂志]]《大观》认为总书记胡锦涛为首的[[中国共产党|中国共产党]]领导层控制[[舆论|舆论]]与强行镇压被中共官方所认定的[[邪教|邪教]]组织<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.parade.com/dictators/2009/ |title=独裁者排行榜 |access-date=2020-08-17 |archive-date=2009-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091015133419/http://www.parade.com/dictators/2009/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在其2005年的十大[[独裁者|独裁者]]排名栏目中，将胡列第四名，2006年降至第六，其后数年均名列十名内<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.voachinese.com/content/a-21-w2006-01-22-voa13-57836987/1058886.html |title = 美杂志列十大独裁者胡锦涛排第六 |language = zh |website = Voachinese.com |date = 2006-01-22 |accessdate = 2017-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306112006/http://www.voachinese.com/content/a-21-w2006-01-22-voa13-57836987/1058886.html |archive-date = 2016-03-06 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[無國界記者|無國界記者]]指責胡錦濤以「[[和諧社會|和諧社會]]」為藉口阻止[[中國|中國]]出現自由[[傳播媒體|媒體]]，把胡錦濤列入「[[新聞自由掠奪者|新聞自由掠奪者]]」名單<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/china/2010/05/100503_rsf_press_freedom.shtml 胡錦濤再上[[新聞自由|新聞自由]]「掠奪者」名單] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/china/2010/05/100503_rsf_press_freedom.shtml |date=20100513005949 }} BBC 2010年5月3日</ref>。2012年，「無國界記者」报道，中共中央總書記胡錦濤下令囚禁68名網民和30名記者，是囚禁新聞自由捍衛者最多的領導人之一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/rolling_news/2012/05/120503_rolling_wpd_china.shtml |title=人權組織批胡錦濤踐踏新聞自由 |publisher=Bbc.co.uk |date=1970-01-01 |accessdate=2017-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120506081810/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/rolling_news/2012/05/120503_rolling_wpd_china.shtml |archive-date=2012-05-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==2010年玉树地震相关争议==
{{main|2010年玉树地震}} 
[[File:Yushuquake-Gruschke1.jpg|thumb]]后扭曲的房屋]]

2010年4月14日上午，[[玉樹|玉樹]]發生[[2010年玉樹地震|7.1級地震]]，地震造成2698人死亡，失踪270人，12135人受伤。縣城[[結古鎮|結古鎮]]全部停電，由於大部分建築都是土木結構，重災區結古鎮附近西杭村的民屋几乎全部（99%）倒塌<ref>{{cite news|language=Zh-hans|url=http://news.163.com/10/0414/13/64819KB7000146BD.html|title=青海玉树地震一村庄夷为平地 99%民房全部倒塌|work=中新社|publisher=网易|date=2010-04-14|accessdate=2010-04-14|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100419002639/http://news.163.com/10/0414/13/64819KB7000146BD.html|archivedate=2010-04-19}}</ref>。此外整个玉树州的70%学校房屋垮塌<ref>{{cite news|language=Zh-hans|title="玉树州红十字会称玉树70%学校房屋垮塌"|url=http://news.163.com/10/0414/22/6491G37K0001124J.html|work=中国广播网|publisher=网易|date=2010-04-14|accessdate=2010-04-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100418070802/http://news.163.com/10/0414/22/6491G37K0001124J.html|archivedate=2010-04-18}}</ref>。

台湾《[[自由时报|自由时报]]》批评中国大陆官方媒体的“单方面报道”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/10/4/19/n2882152.htm|title=青海地震中的人祸|work=自由时报|date=2010-04-19|accessdate=2010-04-26|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100425032436/http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/10/4/19/n2882152.htm|archivedate=2010-04-25}}</ref>。日本《[[朝日新闻|朝日新闻]]》英文版称，[[中共中央宣传部|中共中央宣传部]]已下达“救灾报导禁令” <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/world/2010/04/100416_china_japan_quake.shtml|title=日媒：中宣部限制玉树救灾报道|work=BBC|date=2010-04-16|accessdate=2010-04-17|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100419141147/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/world/2010/04/100416_china_japan_quake.shtml|archivedate=2010-04-19}}</ref>。另有西方媒体则批评中国救援人员消极对待救援，称中国政府少报或“操纵”了伤亡人数，并估计死亡人数应超过一万人。美国《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》则对中国救援力量将救援集中于人员密集的玉树县城表示不满，指出更应主要顾及周边乡镇的民房<ref>{{cite web|publisher=纽约时报|date=2010-04-17|accessdate=2010-04-18|title=After Quake, Ethnic Tibetans Distrust China’s Help|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/04/18/world/asia/18quake.html|author=ANDREW JACOBS|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100422185432/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/04/18/world/asia/18quake.html|archivedate=2010-04-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www1.voanews.com/chinese/news/china/-China-Quake-Relief-Questioned-20100419-91465499.html|title=外国媒体称喇嘛救灾贡献被忽略报道|work=美国之音|date=2010-04-19|accessdate=2010-04-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100423072806/http://www1.voanews.com/chinese/news/china/-China-Quake-Relief-Questioned-20100419-91465499.html|archivedate=2010-04-23}}</ref>。[[美联社|美联社]]认为中国政府“消极对待救援”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2010/04/100417_china_quake_funeral.shtml|title=青海玉树地震死难者集体超度火化|work=BBC|date=2010-04-17|accessdate=2010-04-17|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100420083520/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2010/04/100417_china_quake_funeral.shtml|archivedate=2010-04-20}}</ref>。[[美国之音|美国之音]]同时指责中国政府婉拒其他国家和国际非政府组织派遣专业救援队伍援助青海地震的请求，指称中国政府拒绝境外救援力量是为了“严防境外敌对势力”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www1.voanews.com/chinese/news/china/20100421-China-Refusal-of-Foreign-Aid-for-Earthquake-91698304.html|title=玉树地震拒绝外援 严防境外敌对势力|work=美国之音|date=2010-04-21|accessdate=2010-04-23|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100423174642/http://www1.voanews.com/chinese/news/china/20100421-China-Refusal-of-Foreign-Aid-for-Earthquake-91698304.html|archivedate=2010-04-23}}</ref>。

美国之音批评中国中央政府为玉树地震举行的悼念活动，认为对灾区的悼念是“当局企图转移民众对其他社会问题不满的一种手法”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www1.voanews.com/chinese/news/china/National_Mourn_for_Qinghai_victims_-_a_review_on_administrative_orders-20100421-91691284.html|title=中国全国哀悼引发公民权利争论|work=美国之音|date=2010-04-21|accessdate=2010-04-23|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100423090542/http://www1.voanews.com/chinese/news/china/National_Mourn_for_Qinghai_victims_-_a_review_on_administrative_orders-20100421-91691284.html|archivedate=2010-04-23}}</ref>。[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]引述异议作家[[扎加|扎加]]等8名知識分子的话，对中國政府的救災行動表示批评，並呼籲不要將捐款交給中國官方救援機構，“以防貪污”。其后又报道称扎加因此被捕<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/china/2010/04/100426_tibet_zhogsdung.shtml |title=中國警方逮捕批評政府的青海藏族作家 |access-date=2020-08-17 |archive-date=2019-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822055437/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/china/2010/04/100426_tibet_zhogsdung.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://big5.soundofhope.org/programs/162/157611-1.asp |title=親中共知名藏族作家遭拘捕 |access-date=2020-08-17 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304192909/http://big5.soundofhope.org/programs/162/157611-1.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

